### 集群热重载接口示例
### 使用说明：
### 1. 先启动 MySQL、Redis 和本 demo 服务。
### 2. 重载后测试文件放在 src/main/java/io/github/hotreload/demo/test/reload-after。
### 3. 调用 discover 后，再调用 nodes，把返回的真实节点 IP 填到 targetIp。
### 4. create 接口没有返回 taskId，可通过日志分页接口或数据库拿到 taskId 后填入下面变量。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@appName = cluster-hot-reload-demo
@targetIp = 198.18.0.1
@taskId = STOP-20260701135904-2899e9d1

### 1. 查询可热重载应用列表
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/apps
Accept: application/json


### 2. 刷新目标应用节点信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/discover?appName={{appName}}
Accept: application/json


### 3. 查询目标应用节点列表
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/nodes?appName={{appName}}
Accept: application/json


### 4. 查询当前节点信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/currentNode
Accept: application/json


### 5. 创建集群热重载任务：根据 .class 后缀识别 Service 实现类
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/task/create
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Accept: application/json

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="TestHotReloadServiceImpl.class"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ../src/main/java/io/github/hotreload/demo/test/reload-after/TestHotReloadServiceImpl.class
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="request"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appName": "{{appName}}",
  "persistOnRestart": "N",
  "ips": [
    "{{targetIp}}"
  ],
  "taskRemark": "演示集群热重载 class"
}
--WebAppBoundary--


### 6. 创建集群热重载任务：根据 .class 后缀识别工具类
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/task/create
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Accept: application/json

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="TestHotReloadUtil.class"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ../src/main/java/io/github/hotreload/demo/test/reload-after/TestHotReloadUtil.class
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="request"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appName": "{{appName}}",
  "persistOnRestart": "Y",
  "ips": [
    "{{targetIp}}"
  ],
  "taskRemark": "演示集群热重载普通工具类"
}
--WebAppBoundary--


### 7. 创建集群热重载任务：根据 .xml 后缀识别 MyBatis Mapper XML
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/task/create
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Accept: application/json

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="TestHotReloadMapper.xml"
Content-Type: application/xml

< ../src/main/java/io/github/hotreload/demo/test/reload-after/TestHotReloadMapper.xml
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="request"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appName": "{{appName}}",
  "persistOnRestart": "Y",
  "ips": [
    "{{targetIp}}"
  ],
  "taskRemark": "演示集群热重载 MyBatis Mapper XML"
}
--WebAppBoundary--


### 8. 创建集群热重载任务：重启后保持本次热重载
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/task/create
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Accept: application/json

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="TestHotReloadServiceImpl.class"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ../src/main/java/io/github/hotreload/demo/test/reload-after/TestHotReloadServiceImpl.class
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="request"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appName": "{{appName}}",
  "persistOnRestart": "Y",
  "ips": [
    "{{targetIp}}"
  ],
  "taskRemark": "演示集群热重载并保存重启恢复文件"
}
--WebAppBoundary--


### 9. 查询热重载相关任务详情
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/task/get
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "taskId": "{{taskId}}"
}


### 10. 分页查询热重载相关任务日志
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/task/log/page
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "pageStart": 1,
  "pageNums": 10,
  "requestVo": {
    "appName": "{{appName}}",
    "env": "local",
    "reloadType": ""
  }
}


### 11. 按节点实例状态查询失败日志
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/task/log/page
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "pageStart": 1,
  "pageNums": 10,
  "requestVo": {
    "appName": "{{appName}}",
    "ip": "{{targetIp}}",
    "instanceStatus": "FAILED",
    "executeType": "NORMAL"
  }
}


### 12. 重试失败节点
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/task/retry
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "taskId": "{{taskId}}",
  "ips": [
    "{{targetIp}}"
  ]
}


### 13. 停止目标节点的重启自动恢复（*全部热重载内容）
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/restartRecovery/stop
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "appName": "{{appName}}",
  "fileType": "*",
  "ips": [
    "{{targetIp}}"
  ],
  "taskRemark": "演示停止全部热重载内容的重启自动恢复"
}


### 14. 停止目标节点 class 热重载内容的重启自动恢复
POST {{baseUrl}}/hotReloadCluster/restartRecovery/stop
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "appName": "{{appName}}",
  "fileType": "CLASS",
  "ips": [
    "{{targetIp}}"
  ],
  "taskRemark": "演示只停止 class 热重载内容的重启自动恢复"
}
